I remember when AA first came out.  I saved up all the points for SCM1, 2, and 3, and did hundreds of in-game trials, first casting before taking any spell casting mastery, then with just the first level, then the second, then the third, and taking all the data to figure out how it worked and how much mana it saved, then posting the results.
<br />

<br />
I remember when the new focus item effects first came out.  I remember swapping the summoned focus gear in and out, even going so far as to change other items that I was wearing so that my INT and +MANA remained constant, again casting hundreds of spells in order to determine what the focus effects did, and again, collecting all the data, analyzing, summarizing, and sharing the results here in this forum.
<br />

<br />
